<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Ga Jariri, Ga Jariri LW410</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1) Ga jariri, ga jariri.
 An haife shi a Birnin Dauda.
 Shi ne Yesu, Shi ne Yesu,
 Almasihu, mai ceton duniya.

[V2]
 2) Mu ɗaukaka shi, mu girmama shi,
 Almasihu, mai ceton duniya.
 Ga shehuna daga gabas.
 Sun kawo kayan zinariya.

[V3]
 3) Mun yi murna, mun yi murna
 Tare da mala'ikansa,
 Mun karƃe shi da farinciki
 Don ya zama Madogararmu.

[V4]
 4) Allah Ya yi Ƙaunar duniya
 Har Ya bada mai ceto, Yesu.
 Halleluya, halleluya,
 Halleluya, ga Almasihu.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>410</hymn_number>
</song>